#: ../../docs/classes/class_label.rst:14
msgid ""
"Displays plain text in a line or wrapped inside a rectangle. For "
"formatted text, use :ref:`RichTextLabel <class_RichTextLabel>`."
msgstr "在一行中或在一个矩形中显示纯文本。对于格式化的文本，请使用 :ref:`RichTextLabel <class_RichTextLabel>`。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_label.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_label.rst:19
msgid ""
"Label displays plain text on the screen. It gives you control over the "
"horizontal and vertical alignment, and can wrap the text inside the "
"node's bounding rectangle. It doesn't support bold, italics or other "
"formatting. For that, use :ref:`RichTextLabel <class_RichTextLabel>` "
"instead."
msgstr ""
"标签在屏幕上显示纯文本。它使您可以控制水平和垂直对齐方式，并且可以将文本包装在节点的边界矩形内。它不支持粗体、斜体或其他格式。为此，请改用 "
":ref:`RichTextLabel <class_RichTextLabel>`。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_label.rst:21
msgid ""
"**Note:** Contrarily to most other :ref:`Control <class_Control>`\\ s, "
"Label's :ref:`Control.mouse_filter <class_Control_property_mouse_filter>`"
" defaults to :ref:`Control.MOUSE_FILTER_IGNORE "
"<class_Control_constant_MOUSE_FILTER_IGNORE>` (i.e. it doesn't react to "
"mouse input events). This implies that a label won't display any "
"configured :ref:`Control.hint_tooltip "
"<class_Control_property_hint_tooltip>`, unless you change its mouse "
"filter."
msgstr ""
"**注意**：与大多数其他 :ref:`Control <class_Control>` 相反，标签 ``Label`` 的 "
":ref:`Control.mouse_filter <class_Control_property_mouse_filter>`，默认为 "
":ref:`Control.MOUSE_FILTER_IGNORE "
"<class_Control_constant_MOUSE_FILTER_IGNORE>` "
"（即，对鼠标输入事件无反应）。这意味着标签将不会显示，任何已配置的 :ref:`Control.hint_tooltip "
"<class_Control_property_hint_tooltip>`，除非您更改其鼠标过滤器。"

